  "heading_path": "机械振动 / 阻尼振动",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 54,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01686:2fb0891c3cd1]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01687:0f51a2b70b43]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01688:fb57d6047c63]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01689:45c14f9406df]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01690:6e8c618806ba]]\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01691:1d6a60d17fe0]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01692:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n阻尼很弱，先算无阻尼固有角频率和衰减系数：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01693:6dad971635da]]\n弱阻尼下 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01694:a68a4080449a]]，振动频率几乎不变。振幅 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01695:72d87f14ff3e]]，衰减到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01696:8a3566bccb08]] 时 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01697:daeb8260c5cf]]，即 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01698:dc49e080164c]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01699:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
